ological Basis of Therapeutics. 8th ed." New York, NY: Pergamon Press Inc. (1990):[8] Warrington SJ, Ankier SI, Turner P "Evaluation of possible interactions between ethanol and trazodone or amitriptyline." Neuropsychobiology 15 (1986): 31-7[9] "Product Information. Rexulti (brexpiprazole)." Otsuka American Pharmaceuticals Inc, Rockville, MD.', 1767369485);
